	hr
	.content
		h4 Quick start
		p
			strong CoderStyle
			|  is syntax highlighting project for web developper , very easy to include and integrate in your awesome web application .
			br
			b Last version 
			| : 
			span v0.1
			br
			b Languages supported 
			| : 
			span html
			|  , 
			span css
			br
			b Templates available 
			| : 
			span Monokai
			|  , 
			span Eiffel
			|  , 
			span Solarized
			|  , 
			span Twilight
		h4 Install
		p
			| Very easy to include in your application , just 
			a(href='https://github.com/marwenhlaoui/LoadImg/archive/master.zip') download
			|  or clone from github
			.coderStyle git clone https://github.com/marwenhlaoui/CoderStyle.git 
		hr
		h4 Using
		p
			| You will need to include the template 
			code cs-monokai.min.css
			|  and the script
			code coderstyle.min.js
			|  files you downloaded or by cdn in your layout or pages. 
			.coderStyle(cs-lang='html')
				| <!DOCTYPE html>
				| <html>
				| <head>
				| ...
				// coderstyle css template monokai
				link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='dist/css/tmp/cs-monokai.min.css')
				| 	...
				| </head>
				| <body>
				| 	...
				// JQueryCDN
				script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js')
				| 	...
				// coderstyle js
				script(type='text/javascript', src='dist/js/js-coderstyle.js')
				| 	...
				| </body>
				| </html>
